    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the meatballs are cooking, grate the<strong> lighter cheese</strong></p><p>Remove the dish from the oven after 20 min and top with the <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Return the <strong>lighter</strong> <strong>cheesy courgetti & lean beef meatball bake</strong> to the oven and cook for a final 5 min or until the cheese has melted</p><p>Wash the <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
