    {
      "instruction": "<p>Set the <strong>lighter</strong> <strong>cheesy courgetti & beef meatball bake</strong> in the centre of the table</p><p>Serve the <strong>salad </strong>to the side, dressed with the <strong>remaining balsamic vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a crack of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped basil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
